a warning against islamo - fascism this book is a brilliant expose of islamic fundamentalism and arab culture , showing its threat to western civilisation.a true wake-up call to all who think safety can be found in appeasement.brigitte gabriel 's credibilty is impeccable since she speaks as a christian arab who has experienced islamic terror and israeli democracy.she also gives the lie to the theory that israel is the root cause of international terror . brigitte gabriel is a brave beacon of light whom i salute as a truly righteous gentile